\dfrac{\text{d}x_n}{\text{d}V_a}= \dfrac{1}{N_d} \left(\dfrac{\varepsilon_s}{2q(\frac{1}{N_a}+\frac{1}{N_d})(\phi_i -V_a)}\right)^{1/2}
 \left\{\begin{align} x_d &= x_n \left( 1+ \frac{N_d}{N_a} \right) \\ x_d &=\sqrt{ \frac{2\varepsilon}{q}\left(\frac{1}{N_a}+\frac{1}{N_d}\right)(\phi_i -V_a)} \end{align}\right. 
